# Visual Style Overhaul — Walkthrough

## Changes Made

### 1. Pencil-Sketch Character ([character.js](file:///c:/Users/lilia/OneDrive%20-%20IPSA/Documents/Perso/0%20-%20Projets/Memoir%20maurice/js/character.js))
- Replaced all `MeshStandardMaterial` with `MeshBasicMaterial` in sepia/brown tones (flat color, no lighting reaction)
