- Loading screen updated to parchment tones (`#f4ecd8`)
- Imported fonts: **Caveat** (handwritten) + **EB Garamond** (serif)

### 3. Pedestals with Grimoires ([world.js](file:///c:/Users/lilia/OneDrive%20-%20IPSA/Documents/Perso/0%20-%20Projets/Memoir%20maurice/js/world.js))
